{"tid":2167967,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)災難系列","createTime":"2020-08-21T12:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T20:25:15.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9ffd8f3715857660418c17064cedb67d593c7b","tid":2167967,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=1a8748a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=8cb8053e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=e1831ea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://img31.mtime.cn/mt/2014/02/22/231940.76432374_270X405X4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg31.mtime.cn%2Fmt%2F2014%2F02%2F22%2F231940.76432374_270X405X4.jpg&h=7049c8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/58/The_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F58%2FThe_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg&h=bc58c67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一場意外的大爆炸把連接紐約曼哈頓和新澤西州的主要隧道封閉，由於爆炸正值下班的交通巔峰期，隧道頓時哀嚎遍野。面臨這場災難的汽車族人人自危，驚惶失措，此時一名叫做奇德的前緊療急救服務中心主任挺身而出；在隧道隨時都可能崩塌之際，奇德以冷靜的頭腦和矯健的身手拯救罹難的人讓他們得以重見天日<br />\n<br />\n2.在一片已經極度融化的南極冰川上，古氣候學家傑克&middot;霍爾與同事弗蘭克和傑森在冰川上考察時，親眼目睹整個拉森冰架全部斷裂。傑克隨後將有關全球暖化調查結果，在新德里舉行的聯合國研討會上作出報告，聲明兩極冰川融化已經阻斷了北大西洋洋流的暖洋流，而這種情況繼續持續下去將會在未來形成另一個冰河時期。但參加會議的各國元首對此感到荒謬，美國副總統雷蒙&middot;貝克甚至把傑克的理論當作笑話看待..<br />\n<br />\n3.2009年，太陽系八大行星經過幾千年的周期後排列成了一條直線，太陽發生了一場歷史上規模最大的太陽爆發。在印度，美國地質學家艾德禮安&middot;赫姆斯利來到堪稱世界最深的銅礦場接見了天文物理學家薩南，而薩南展示太陽爆發導致中微子的數量破表，甚至產生物理反應而開始加熱地球的核心，在未來即將導致整個板塊全部崩潰。艾德禮安馬上回華盛頓見了白宮幕僚長卡爾&middot;安修瑟，卡爾在極爲震驚下將此事彙報給美國總統湯瑪斯&middot;威爾森<br />\n<br />\n8 25PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=ff5605ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=496f7f16\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f00e441adfbd4150f072af57f004d45c30fba8e","tid":2167967,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:23:43.000